WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.164
Seventy-seven percent of Porsche customers prefer text updates. Text is fast, convenient, and

00:00:05.214 --> 00:00:09.976
respectful of their time — but it carries no tone of voice.

00:00:10.026 --> 00:00:15.190
Use it for short, confirmable updates. Never for bad news or complex explanations.
